- What are you doing? Mr. Pei!

307
00:11:47,900 --> 00:11:48,470
Mr. Pei!

308
00:11:48,470 --> 00:11:49,380
I won't be taking it.

309
00:11:49,380 --> 00:11:50,500
- Go!
- This is too much!

310
00:11:50,500 --> 00:11:50,780
Go!

311
00:11:50,780 --> 00:11:51,470
Mr. Ma!

312
00:11:51,590 --> 00:11:52,780
