316
00:11:56,620 --> 00:11:58,380
Fine. You won't be able to take it.

317
00:11:58,380 --> 00:11:59,020
I'll get a ride.

318
00:11:59,020 --> 00:12:00,140
I'm not taking the bus.

319
00:12:00,140 --> 00:12:01,470
Go get a ride!

320
00:12:01,590 --> 00:12:02,470
Li!

321
