382
00:15:02,702 --> 00:15:04,902
There'll always be a time
when we have to part.

383
00:15:06,380 --> 00:15:07,540
This is enough.

384
00:15:07,710 --> 00:15:08,620
I don't want to become

385
00:15:08,620 --> 00:15:09,830
