410
00:16:07,620 --> 00:16:09,260
I'll go and make an application.

411
00:16:10,310 --> 00:16:12,190
Lin Wan, sorry.

412
00:16:12,310 --> 00:16:14,430
I haven't read your proposal.

413
00:16:14,830 --> 00:16:15,780
However, I believe

414
00:16:15,780 --> 00:16:18,140
