who came to cause trouble?

465
00:19:38,910 --> 00:19:39,670
Qian!

466
00:19:42,260 --> 00:19:42,910
Thank you!

467
00:19:42,910 --> 00:19:43,910
Thank you, everyone.

468
00:19:44,080 --> 00:19:45,710
