with relevant experience.

893
00:37:18,620 --> 00:37:21,180
Even a small web store
does background checks?

894
00:37:26,470 --> 00:37:27,430
Hello, Mr. Pei.

895
00:37:27,660 --> 00:37:28,750
I want to know

896
00:37:28,750 --> 00:37:29,580
